<ol>
  <li>From the <%= SITE_NAME %> homepage, click on <%= link_to "Current Classes", klasses_path %>.</li>
  <li>Click on the class name.</li>
  <li>Click <strong>Register</strong>:</li>
      <%= image_tag("register.png", {:border => 1, :width => "80%", :height => "80%", :title=>"register"})%>
      <p>
  <li>If the class has multiple sections, click the <strong>section name</strong> to reveal a drop down box.</li>
  <li> Select the section you plan to attend.</li>
  <p>
    <p>
      <%= image_tag("select_section.png", {:border => 1, :width => "60%", :height => "60%", :title=>"select section"})%>
    <p>
  <li>Optional: if instructor has enabled this setting, you have the option to enter your university/student ID.</li>
  <li>Optional: if you wish to audit, mark the audit box.</li>
  <li>Click <strong>Create Registration Request</strong> to send your request to the instructor.</li>
</ol>
<p>You will be notified if the instructor approves your request.</p>
